Text.Value: How many more of you are there?
Why did you want this dagger so much?
*The corpse remains silent. It does not know.*

EditorData.logicalname: DOESN'T KNOW ANSWER - DELETE IF NOT NEEDED

Text.Value: I found this flowery key. What is it for?
*The corpse tries to speak, but something prevents it.*
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*

Synopsis: SwD with one of the Shifters that were sent to retrieve the dagger of the serial killer from the tunnels underneath the Open Hand temple.
